articles.title: About the Course
articles.contents:
This course is DACSS 601: Data Science Fundamentals. In this course, we give you exposure to the basic tools you will need to conduct data analysis in R.
Course Instructor:
Curtis Atkisson

              Learning R so far has been a challenge but with lots of hands-on practice it’ll get easier. Fingers crossed.
